],["^15",[53,"^K",1735680266325,536870919]],["^15",[53,"^[",52,536870919]],["^15",[53,"^@",false,536870919]],["^15",[53,"^Y","git",536870919]],["^15",[53,"^11","Git",536870919]],["^15",[53,"^B",1735680266325,536870919]],["^15",[53,"^;","~u6774610a-ae4c-4569-86d3-fee369068a57",536870919]],["^15",[54,"^Q","Ignore file locally: `git update-index --assume-unchanged PATH`",536870919]],["^15",[54,"^O","^16",536870919]],["^15",[54,"^F",53,536870919]],["^15",[54,"^X",53,536870919]],["^15",[54,"^V",53,536870919]],["^15",[54,"^U",53,536870919]],["^15",[54,"^;","~u6774610a-91f5-4060-9009-2d1f69b17060",536870919]],["^15",[55,"^3","- Media-Center\n\t- ```yaml\n\t  services:\n\t  \n\t    gluetun:\n\t      image: qmcgaw/gluetun\n\t      container_name: gluetun\n\t      cap_add:\n\t        - NET_ADMIN\n\t      devices:\n\t        - /dev/net/tun:/dev/net/tun\n\t      ports:\n\t        - 8888:8888/tcp # HTTP proxy\n\t        - 8388:8388/tcp # Shadowsocks\n\t        - 8388:8388/udp # Shadowsocks\n\t        - 7878:7878 # Radarr\n\t        - 8989:8989 # Sonarr\n\t        - 9696:9696 # Prowlarr\n\t        - 8080:8080 # Qbit\n\t        - 6881:6881 # Qbit\n\t        - 6881:6881/udp # Qbit\n\t        - 3000:3000 # LF\n\t        - 3001:3001 # LF\n\t      environment:\n\t        - VPN_SERVICE_PROVIDER=nordvpn\n\t        - VPN_TYPE=wireguard\n\t        - WIREGUARD_PRIVATE_KEY=YKSZEanrrEiH8pty2y7cvxvxRRK5uzC78K7xFMXwKWQ=\n\t        - SERVER_COUNTRIES=Netherlands\n\t        - TZ=New_York\n\t        - UPDATER_PERIOD=24h\n\t      restart: unless-stopped\n\t    \n\t    radarr:\n\t      image: lscr.io/linuxserver/radarr:latest\n\t      container_name: radarr\n\t      network_mode: \"service:gluetun\"\n\t      environment:\n\t        - PUID=1000\n\t        - PGID=1000\n\t        - TZ=Etc/UTC\n\t      volumes:\n\t        - /nas-storage/configs/radarr:/config\n\t        - /media-storage/movies:/movies\n\t        - /media-storage/downloads:/downloads\n\t      restart: unless-stopped\n\t  \n\t    sonarr:\n\t      image: lscr.io/linuxserver/sonarr:latest\n\t      container_name: sonarr\n\t      network_mode: \"service:gluetun\"\n\t      environment:\n\t        - PUID=1000\n\t        - PGID=1000\n\t        - TZ=Etc/UTC\n\t      volumes:\n\t        - /path/to/sonarr/data:/config\n\t        - /path/to/tvseries:/tv\n\t        - /media-storage/downloads:/downloads\n\t      restart: unless-stopped\n\t  \n\t    prowlarr:\n\t      image: lscr.io/linuxserver/prowlarr:latest\n\t      container_name: prowlarr\n\t      network_mode: \"service:gluetun\"\n\t      environment:\n\t        - PUID=1000\n\t        - PGID=1000\n\t        - TZ=Etc/UTC\n\t      restart: unless-stopped\n\t  \n\t    qbittorrent:\n\t      image: lscr.io/linuxserver/qbittorrent:latest\n\t      container_name: qbittorrent\n\t      network_mode: \"service:gluetun\"\n\t      environment:\n\t        - PUID=1000\n\t        - PGID=1000\n\t        - TZ=Etc/UTC\n\t        - WEBUI_PORT=8080\n\t        - TORRENTING_PORT=6881\n\t      volumes:\n\t        - /nas-storage/configs/qbit:/config\n\t        - /media-storage/downloads:/downloads\n\t      restart: unless-stopped\n\t  \n\t    jellyfin:\n\t      image: lscr.io/linuxserver/jellyfin:latest\n\t      container_name: jellyfin\n\t      environment:\n\t        - PUID=1000\n\t        - PGID=1000\n\t        - TZ=Etc/UTC\n\t      volumes:\n\t        - /nas-storage/configs/jellyfin:/config\n\t        - /media-storage/tv:/data/tvshows\n\t        - /media-storage/movies:/data/movies\n\t      ports:\n\t        - 8096:8096\n\t      restart: unless-stopped\n\t  ```",536870919]],["^15",[55,"^17",1735680266339,536870919]],["^15",[55,"^Z","pages/HomeLab.md",536870919]],["^15",[56,"^K",1735680266338,536870919]],["^15",[56,"^[",55,536870919]],["^15",[56,"^@",false,536870919]],["^15",[56,"^Y","homelab",536870919]],["^15",[56,"^11","HomeLab",536870919]],["^15",[56,"^B",1735680266338,536870919]],["^15",[56,"^;","~u6774610a-9481-469f-bd4a-2dee818fb533",536870919]],["^15",[57,"^Q","Media-Center",536870919]],["^15",[57,"^O","^16",536870919]],["^15",[57,"^F",56,536870919]],["^15",[57,"^X",56,536870919]],["^15",[57,"^V",56,536870919]],["^15",[57,"^U",56,536870919]],["^15",[57,"^;","~u6774610a-717f-411b-b541-6b1ab9c1c459",536870919]],["^15",[58,"^Q","~```yaml\nservices:\n\n  gluetun:\n    image: qmcgaw/gluetun\n    container_name: gluetun\n    cap_add:\n      - NET_ADMIN\n    devices:\n      - /dev/net/tun:/dev/net/tun\n    ports:\n      - 8888:8888/tcp # HTTP proxy\n      - 8388:8388/tcp # Shadowsocks\n      - 8388:8388/udp # Shadowsocks\n      - 7878:7878 # Radarr\n      - 8989:8989 # Sonarr\n      - 9696:9696 # Prowlarr\n      - 8080:8080 # Qbit\n      - 6881:6881 # Qbit\n      - 6881:6881/udp # Qbit\n      - 3000:3000 # LF\n      - 3001:3001 # LF\n    environment:\n      - VPN_SERVICE_PROVIDER=nordvpn\n      - VPN_TYPE=wireguard\n      - WIREGUARD_PRIVATE_KEY=YKSZEanrrEiH8pty2y7cvxvxRRK5uzC78K7xFMXwKWQ=\n      - SERVER_COUNTRIES=Netherlands\n      - TZ=New_York\n      - UPDATER_PERIOD=24h\n    restart: unless-stopped\n  \n  radarr:\n    image: lscr.io/linuxserver/radarr:latest\n    container_name: radarr\n    network_mode: \"service:gluetun\"\n    environment:\n      - PUID=1000\n      - PGID=1000\n      - TZ=Etc/UTC\n    volumes:\n      - /nas-storage/configs/radarr:/config\n      - /media-storage/movies:/movies\n      - /media-storage/downloads:/downloads\n    restart: unless-stopped\n\n  sonarr:\n    image: lscr.io/linuxserver/sonarr:latest\n    container_name: sonarr\n    network_mode: \"service:gluetun\"\n    environment:\n      - PUID=1000\n      - PGID=1000\n      - TZ=Etc/UTC\n    volumes:\n      - /path/to/sonarr/data:/config\n      - /path/to/tvseries:/tv\n      - /media-storage/downloads:/downloads\n    restart: unless-stopped\n\n  prowlarr:\n    image: lscr.io/linuxserver/prowlarr:latest\n    container_name: prowlarr\n    network_mode: \"service:gluetun\"\n    environment:\n      - PUID=1000\n      - PGID=1000\n      - TZ=Etc/UTC\n    restart: unless-stopped\n\n  qbittorrent:\n    image: lscr.io/linuxserver/qbittorrent:latest\n    container_name: qbittorrent\n    network_mode: \"service:gluetun\"\n    environment:\n      - PUID=1000\n      - PGID=1000\n      - TZ=Etc/UTC\n      - WEBUI_PORT=8080\n      - TORRENTING_PORT=6881\n    volumes:\n      - /nas-storage/configs/qbit:/config\n      - /media-storage/downloads:/downloads\n    restart: unless-stopped\n\n  jellyfin:\n    image: lscr.io/linuxserver/jellyfin:latest\n    container_name: jellyfin\n    environment:\n      - PUID=1000\n      - PGID=1000\n      - TZ=Etc/UTC\n    volumes:\n      - /nas-storage/configs/jellyfin:/config\n      - /media-storage/tv:/data/tvshows\n      - /media-storage/movies:/data/movies\n    ports:\n      - 8096:8096\n    restart: unless-stopped\n```",536870919]],["^15",[58,"^O","^16",536870919]],["^15",[58,"^F",57,536870919]],["^15",[58,"^X",56,536870919]],["^15",[58,"^V",57,536870919]],["^15",[58,"^U",56,536870919]],["^15",[58,"^;","~u6774610a-4109-4825-ab34-42740c1ced6e",536870919]],["^15",[59,"^3","- Serveur test avec [[Docker]]\n\t- ``docker build -t ricard-alma ./alma/FakeServer/``\n\t- ``docker run --privileged --network=host -ti --name=\"ricard-alma\" -d -v $(pwd):/ricard  ricard-alma``\n\t- ``docker exec -it ricard-alma /bin/bash`` *optionel*\n\t- ``docker exec -it ricard-alma /ricard/alma/FakeServer/run.sh``\n-\n- Vrai serveur\n\t- Update\n\t\t- Update sécurité -> chaque 6 mois\n\t\t- Update complete + reboot -> chaque premier septembre (montré sur le dashboard)\n\t\t- Update watchtower -> chaque 2 mois\n\t\t- Nettoyage fichier -> chaque semaines\n\t- Commandes Bash utilisé dans le script\n\t\t- Espace disque (%): ``stat -f / | grep -E \"Blocks\" | awk '{printf \"%.2f%%\\n\", (($3 - $5) / $3) * 100}'``\n\t\t- Espace utilisé: ``stat -f / | grep -E \"Blocks\" | awk '{print $5}'``\n\t\t  id:: 67659fa0-6a03-4da8-97a7-2b36bec835b5\n\t\t- Espace total: ``stat -f / | grep -E \"Blocks\" | awk '{print $3}'``\n-\n- [[Ansib